-- Bank of Japan Will Buy 100 Billion Yen of Commercial Paper for Asset Fund
-- B y   N a o t o   H o s o d a
-- 2010-12-10T00:36:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-10/bank-of-japan-will-buy-100-billion-yen-of-commercial-paper-for-asset-fund.html
The Bank of Japan will buy 100
billion yen ($1.2 billion) of commercial paper starting on Dec.
15, the central bank said in a statement today. The BOJ in
October created a 5 trillion-yen fund to buy government and
corporate debt as well as riskier instruments including
exchange-traded funds.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Naoto Hosoda at 
 nhosoda@bloomberg.net  